<p>The Sports Federation & Olympic Committee of Hong Kong, China will hold the Olympic Day Run for 2013 on Sunday, June 23 at the Hong Kong Disneyland Resort, starting at 7.45am. <p>Under the patronage of the International Olympic Committee, the Hong Kong NOC will organise a sports carnival by combining the elements of a 5.6-km fun run, display booths, games session, lucky draw and various cultural performances to encourage people from the community to implement the theme “Move, Learn and Discover”. </p></p>